UNITED STATES of America v. Madge NIELSEN et al. No. 5008. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. May 5, 1955. A. Pratt Kesler, U. S. Atty., Llewellyn O. Thomas and C. Nelson Day, Asst. U. S. Attys., Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellant. Nielsen & Conder, Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellees.
